{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/221220/TIL221220/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h2>react memo, useCallback, useMemo</h2>\n<h3>memo</h3>\n<p>memo는 컴포넌트의 불필요한 재 렌더링을 막아준다.</p>\n<p>memo를 사용하면 부모요소의 렌더링 또는 props가 변화될 경우에는, 마지막으로 렌더링된 결과를 재사용 하게 된다.</p>\n<p>변경되지 않는 props는 useCallback등으로 감싸주어야한다.</p>\n<p>컴포넌트 내부에서 useState, useReducer, useContext 훅을 사용하면 여전히 재 렌더링 된다.</p>\n<p>이 메서드는 오직 성능 최적화만들 위해 사용해야한다. 의도적으로 렌더링을 방지하기 위해 사용하면 안된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> MyComponent <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">memo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">MyComponent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">props</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">/* props를 사용하여 렌더링 */</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>useCallback(fn, deps)</h3>\n<p>deps가 변경될 때 내부의 함수를 재 정의 하고자 할 때 사용하는 훅.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> memoizedCallback <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useCallback</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">doSomething</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> b<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> b<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>useMemo(( ) ⇒ fn, deps)</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> memoizedValue <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useMemo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token function\">computeExpensiveValue</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> b<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> b<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>useCallback과 마찬가지로, deps가 변경될 때 변경될 값을 메모이제이션 된 값을 반환하게 된다.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"TIL 221220","summary":"메모제이션을 위한 memo, useMemo, useCallback","date":"2022.12.20.","categories":["TIL","memo","useMemo","useCallback"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/de7eec9dad1f55c711674e15602b601d/9ce37/TIL221220.png","srcSet":"/static/de7eec9dad1f55c711674e15602b601d/e1116/TIL221220.png 384w,\n/static/de7eec9dad1f55c711674e15602b601d/9b7d7/TIL221220.png 768w,\n/static/de7eec9dad1f55c711674e15602b601d/9ce37/TIL221220.png 1536w","sizes":"(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/de7eec9dad1f55c711674e15602b601d/5358b/TIL221220.webp 384w,\n/static/de7eec9dad1f55c711